Lense App Privacy Policy
Last Updated: 21-08-2023
Thank you for choosing Lense. We're committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal data when you use our app.
Information We Collect
Personal Data:
When you register for Lense, we collect your name and email address.
Photos:
All photos you upload to Lense are stored on our servers. These photos belong to you, and we will never resell or use them for any other commercial purposes without your explicit consent.
Tracking & Analytics:
We utilize tracking tools to understand user interactions within our app, primarily for marketing purposes.
Purpose and Legal Basis for Processing
Service Provision:
To provide our services, such as storing and displaying photos.
Communication:
Communicating with you about updates, offers, or essential information related to our services.
Marketing:
Understanding your use of our app to enhance our marketing efforts. The legal basis for this processing is our legitimate interest in understanding our users and offering the best possible service.
Data Sharing
We do not sell your personal data. We only share it under the following circumstances:
With your consent.
We will not share any of your photos, personal information or data linked to you.
Legal requirements
To comply with legal obligations or to protect the rights and properties of Lense, our users, or third parties.
Your Rights Under GDPR
Access & Rectification:
You have the right to request access to and correct your personal data.
Erasure:
You have the right to request the deletion of your personal data, subject to certain exceptions.
Objection:
You can object to our processing of your personal data for marketing purposes at any time.
Data Portability:
ou have the right to request a copy of the personal data we hold about you in a structured, machine-readable format.
Security
We employ suitable security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, modification, disclosure, or destruction.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may occasionally update this Privacy Policy. When we do, we will update the "last updated" date at the top of this policy. It's your responsibility to review this policy regularly.
Contact
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can reach us at support@lense.app.